data.description:
Welcome to your lakeside dream home on Lake Diamond! The true hidden gem of Moore County, located less than 10 minutes from the Village of Pinehurst. Before we go into the home, let's talk about the neighborhood first. Lake Diamond is a gated community, with an approximate 45-acre lake, perfect for fishing, swimming, or taking your electric boat, kayak, or SUP on. The recent completion of a community beach is a great addition, but you really don't need it since this home has its own beach. There are only 31 homes in Lake Diamond and many residents love it for the sense of community there. It is not uncommon to ride your golf cart to a neighbor's house for a party or gathering. Besides lake houses, you will also find numerous horse farms within Lake Diamond's gates.  This custom home was built in 2006 and has so much to offer. The 4257 sq foot residence sits on one acre and has 3 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, 2 rec rooms, and 4 flex rooms suitable for additional bedrooms.  Starting from the ground up, the concrete floored crawlspace is completely conditioned with lights throughout allowing easy access and protection for all housing components located there. The three-car garage easily fits three full size vehicles, has space for a workshop, and also has tons of additional storage with sturdy shelving put along the walls. Inside the garage you will also find the water purifying & softener system and the central vacuum system. Right outside the garage, you will find the auto-start Generac home generator, which runs off propane.  The front porch is expansive and wraps around the side, where you are able to enter the home into the office or the master bedroom. Upon entering the front door, you will find yourself in the foyer where you will see hardwood floors throughout the main living area and freshly painted walls. The home has a formal dining for those gatherings you're sure to have. The spacious kitchen has counter seating for three, an island with an additional two seats, and a built-in desk. The Corian countertops were just redone in December 2023 and look great. The double oven, cooktop, and island with a sink are a home cook's dream. The beautiful views of the lake from the kitchen should prevent most of the complaining from whoever has to do the dishes. Not all, but most. Down the hall from the kitchen, you will find a full bath with a walk-in shower and further down you will find the laundry room with a doggy door that leads to the backyard.

The living room also offers great views of the lake, along with a fireplace and hardwired Bose surround sound system. The oh-so important home office can be found off the living room and has access to the front porch. The office also has a wet bar, which is a great way to wind down after a day of work.

The master bedroom is found on the primary floor and is a true retreat. The large bedroom has a 10' vaulted ceiling, fireplace, and private access to the back deck and the front porch. The master bathroom has a walk-in shower, huge closet, jetted tub, double vanity, and a heated floor, making those cold winter mornings a little more comfortable.

Moving upstairs along the backside of the house, you will find one bedroom, a full bathroom, and three flex rooms, all with water views. Along the frontside of the second story you will find an additional bedroom, flex room, full bathroom, and a large rec room with a wet bar, that has multiple uses. Completing the second story, is a large balcony overlooking the backyard and the lake.

On the third floor, you'll find the last large rec room, currently being used as the ping-pong room, and a utility room, which I like to call the Operations Center. In this room, you will find HVAC components, propane on-demand hot water heater, and telecom/cable panel. In this room, you will also be able to see the type of spray foam insulation that is throughout the exterior of the home. In between interior walls and floors, there is fiberglass batt insulation to help with sound control.

Making our way outside to the fenced in backyard, you will find the large deck constructed in 2020, with hot tub. The 10 zoned irrigation system compliments the well-manicured yard of centipede and Bermuda grass. The beach and dock, also constructed in 2020, round out this perfect backyard.
